content:
Map Your Presence Statuses to Amazon Connect

Keep your agents' busy statuses in sync across Amazon Connect and Omni-Channel. Mapped presence statuses are automatically synced with Amazon Connect for any Omni-Channel presence status change.

REQUIRED USER PERMISSIONS:
Customize Application AND Manage Call Centers (to view the Amazon Contact Centers page)
Contact Center Admin (to create and manage a contact center)

This feature is available with Service Cloud Voice and Partner Telephony from Amazon Connect.

To map your presence statuses:

From Setup, enter Amazon Contact Centers.
Select the contact center.
Under Presence Status Mapping, click Add.
Select an existing busy Omni-Channel presence status.
Specify an existing custom Amazon Connect agent status.
title: Map Presence Status to Amazon Connect
